# Radiance Coaching Center — Flutter App

## Rule: Keep this file current
After **meaningful** code or architecture changes (new features, deps, routes, conventions), **update this section** so AI and humans always see the latest project context. Bump the **Last updated** line below.

**Last updated:** 2026-04-09 (FCM Edge + `scripts/set-fcm-secret.ps1`, in-app notifications, `AppBarDrawerLeading`, community/doubt RLS migrations, rules refresh)

---

## Project Context
Flutter app for **Radiance Coaching Center** (Tongi, Gazipur, Bangladesh). Targets **Android** (primary); admin may use desktop builds. Manages SSC/HSC coaching: admin + student (+ teacher doubt inbox), payments, attendance, exams, community chat, doubts, CMS, etc. See `plan/` for product/DB docs.

## Implementation status (snapshot)
| Area | Status |
|------|--------|
| **App shell** | `main.dart`: `ProviderScope` + `MaterialApp.router`; `initSupabase()` + `FcmService.init()` before `runApp` |
| **Theme** | `lib/app/theme.dart` — Material 3, Hind Siliguri + Nunito, primary/accent tokens; `theme_settings` / `themeSettingsProvider` |
| **Supabase** | `lib/core/supabase_client.dart` — `SUPABASE_URL` / `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` via `--dart-define` or `supabase_bootstrap.dart` fallbacks |
| **Supabase repo** | `supabase/migrations/` — schema + RLS; Edge: `send-notification` (FCM v1), `create-student`, `generate-monthly-dues`, `send-sms` (stubs where noted) |
| **Firebase / FCM** | `lib/firebase_options.dart` (FlutterFire); `android/app/google-services.json`; `lib/core/services/fcm_service.dart` persists `users.fcm_token`; `NotificationEdgeService` invokes `send-notification`; **deploy secret** `FCM_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON` (Firebase service account JSON). **Windows:** PowerShell `Set-Content -Encoding utf8` adds BOM and breaks `supabase secrets set --env-file` — use `scripts/set-fcm-secret.ps1` or `[System.IO.File]::WriteAllText` with `UTF8Encoding` no BOM |
| **AppBar / drawer** | Use `leading: const AppBarDrawerLeading()` (see `lib/app/widgets/app_bar_drawer_leading.dart`). Do **not** pass the screen `State`’s `context` to `appBarDrawerLeading(context)` — `Scaffold` is not an ancestor, so the menu button disappears. Student/Admin/Teacher drawers export `AppBarDrawerLeading` |
| **Routing** | `lib/app/router.dart` — GoRouter; order-sensitive routes (e.g. `/admin/courses/:id/notice` before `/admin/courses/:id`); `/student/notifications`; `/admin/*`, `/teacher/*`, `/student/*` |
| **Auth** | `AuthRepository` + `signInProvider`; post-login `FcmService.syncTokenAfterAuth()` |
| **Notifications (in-app)** | `lib/features/notifications/` — list screen, `NotificationsRepository`, `unreadNotificationCountProvider`; `NotificationAppBarAction` on key student screens; admin **course notice**: `admin_course_notice_screen.dart`, button on course detail |
| **DB triggers** | `20260409280000_message_notification_triggers.sql` — inserts `notifications` rows on community/doubt messages (separate from client-invoked FCM) |
| **Admin dashboard** | `admin_dashboard_screen.dart` — cards, charts, drawer |
| **Admin students** | list + profile + add student |
| **Admin payments** | hub + add/edit payment |
| **Admin attendance** | hub → taking screen |
| **Admin exams** | list, editor, detail; publish → `ResultCalculator` + `invokeSendNotification` |
| **Student app** | dashboard, courses, notes, payments, attendance, results, exams, community, doubts, settings, profile, QBank placeholder |
| **Doubts** | student list/new/chat; staff inbox (admin/teacher); `DoubtChatScreen` — stream empty-guard + refetch after send |
| **Community** | groups + chat; storage bucket `community`; RLS helpers in `20260409270000_community_users_rls_and_storage.sql` |
| **Public / CMS** | `public_home_screen` + `admin_home_cms_screen` |
| **Models** | `shared/models/` |
| **Tests** | `test/` smoke + date SQL test |

## Tech stack

### In use (pubspec)
- Flutter (Dart SDK ^3.11)
- **flutter_riverpod** + **riverpod_annotation**; codegen: **build_runner** + **riverpod_generator**
- **go_router**, **supabase_flutter**, **google_fonts**, **uuid**, **pdf** / **printing**, **share_plus**
- **cached_network_image**, **shimmer**, **image_picker**, **file_picker**, **url_launcher**
- **firebase_core**, **firebase_messaging**, **flutter_local_notifications**
- **dio**, **fl_chart**, **intl**, **path_provider**, **flutter_pdfview**, **flutter_math_fork**, **connectivity_plus**, **shared_preferences**, **youtube_player_flutter**

### Edge / workers
- **`send-notification`:** Deno Edge, `npm:google-auth-library`, FCM HTTP v1; env `FCM_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON`; caller JWT must be admin or teacher; updates `notifications.fcm_sent` matching title+body for sent users
- Other functions: see each `supabase/functions/*/index.ts` header comments

### Scripts (repo)
- `scripts/set-fcm-secret.ps1` — writes `secrets-fcm.env` UTF-8 **no BOM** for `npx supabase secrets set --env-file` (see script for usage)

## Architecture pattern
Feature-first under `lib/features/{feature}/` with repositories for Supabase, Riverpod providers where used.

## Coding standards
- **ConsumerWidget** / **ConsumerStatefulWidget** when using Riverpod for those screens.
- **@riverpod** + generated code where applicable; run `dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs` after provider edits.
- **All Supabase calls** in **repository** classes.
- Bengali UI copy via **GoogleFonts.hindSiliguri()** where specified.

## Supabase & roles
- Phone OTP; `public.users.id` = `auth.users.id`; route guards use JWT metadata `role` (`kRoleAdmin` / `kRoleStudent` / `kRoleTeacher`).

## Database tables
See `plan/03_database_roadmap.md` and `supabase/migrations/`.

## Colors (`lib/app/theme.dart`)
- primary `0xFF1A3C6E`, accent `0xFFF5A623`, surfaces as in theme.

## Language
- **UI copy:** Bengali where specified.
- **Code & comments:** English.

## Git / secrets
- Never commit `*firebase-adminsdk*.json`, `secrets-fcm.env`, or service account keys. `.gitignore` includes these patterns.
